description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 62, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 124, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, 2 for South, and Stringalong for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40622-57272-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [124 Votes, Top 15% Score]
